# PokeManiac Development Checklists

Use these checklists before starting work to ensure nothing is missed.

---

## ✅ Adding a New Feature Module

### Setup
- [ ] Read skill: `pokemaniac-new-feature`
- [ ] Feature name decided (snake_case, e.g., `mynewfeature`)
- [ ] Feature purpose documented

### Directory Structure
- [ ] Created `feature/mynewfeature/` directory
- [ ] Created all subdirectories: `ui/`, `uimodel/`, `di/`, `navigator/`
- [ ] Created `src/test/java/` for tests
- [ ] Created `src/main/res/` for resources (if needed)

### Core Files
- [ ] `MyNewFeatureActivity.kt` - Entry point with PokeManiacTheme
- [ ] `MyNewFeatureScreen.kt` - Container with state collection
- [ ] `MyNewFeatureViewModel.kt` - With sealed UiState, `MutableSharedFlow<UiError>`, no mappers
- [ ] `MyNewFeatureView.kt` - Stateless view with when() on state
- [ ] `MyNewFeatureContent.kt` - Content sections
- [ ] `MyNewFeaturePreview.kt` - Preview composables for all states
- [ ] `uimodel/MyNewFeatureUI.kt` - UI data models **+ their domain→UI mappers** (extension functions)

### Navigation
- [ ] Navigator interface created in `coreui/navigator/`
- [ ] `MyNewFeatureNavigatorImpl.kt` in feature module
- [ ] Intent setup with required extras
- [ ] Registered in Koin module

### Dependency Injection
- [ ] `di/MyNewFeatureModule.kt` created
- [ ] `viewModelOf(::MyNewFeatureViewModel)` binding
- [ ] Navigator bound: `single<MyNewFeatureNavigator> { MyNewFeatureNavigatorImpl() }`

### Gradle Configuration
- [ ] `feature/mynewfeature/build.gradle.kts` created
- [ ] Dependencies: `domain`, `coreui`, `:shared:tracking` (if using `TrackingRepository`), Compose, Koin
- [ ] Added to `settings.gradle.kts`
- [ ] Added dependency to `app/build.gradle.kts`

### Application Integration
- [ ] Module imported in `PokeManiacApplication.kt`
- [ ] Added to Koin modules list: `modules(..., myNewFeatureModule)`
- [ ] Feature Activity reachable from other features

### Imports Verification
- [ ] ❌ NO imports from `:shared:data`, `:shared:api`, or `database` implementation packages
- [ ] ✅ Only imports from `domain`, `coreui` (and not `:shared:tracking` impl types — use `TrackingRepository` from domain)

### Testing
- [ ] `MyNewFeatureViewModelTest.kt` created
- [ ] At least one happy path test
- [ ] Error case test
- [ ] Preview composables included

### Documentation
- [ ] Feature purpose documented
- [ ] Key screens/flows described

---

## ✅ Adding API Endpoint & Data Operations

### Design Phase
- [ ] Endpoint purpose defined
- [ ] Request/response DTOs designed
- [ ] Domain entity model created

### Repository (Domain Layer)
- [ ] Repository interface created: `domain/repositories/My*Repository.kt`
- [ ] Methods defined: `get()`, `search()`, `create()`, `update()`, `delete()`
- [ ] Return types correct: `Flow<>` for reads, `suspend fun` for writes
- [ ] Domain entity created: `domain/entities/MyEntity.kt`

### Data Layer Implementation
- [ ] `data/myentity/MyRepositoryImpl.kt` created
- [ ] Implements domain interface
- [ ] Uses constructor injection for Request + DataStore
- [ ] Handles data merging (local + remote)

### API Layer
- [ ] Retrofit service method added/created
- [ ] DTO created with @Serializable (Moshi)
- [ ] `api/myentity/MyRequestImpl.kt` created
- [ ] Implements `MyRequest` interface
- [ ] DTOs properly mapped to domain entities

### Database Layer
- [ ] Room entity created: `database/myentity/MyEntityBase.kt`
- [ ] DAO created: `database/myentity/MyEntityDao.kt`
- [ ] Methods: `getAll()`, `getById()`, `insert()`, `update()`, `delete()`
- [ ] `database/myentity/MyDataStoreImpl.kt` created
- [ ] Implements `MyDataStore` interface
- [ ] Entities properly mapped to/from domain models

### Koin Registration
- [ ] Updated `dependencyinjection/CleanArchiModules.kt`:
  - [ ] `dataModule`: Add `factory<MyRepository> { MyRepositoryImpl(...) }`
  - [ ] `apiModule`: Add `factory<MyRequest> { MyRequestImpl(...) }`
  - [ ] `databaseModule`: Add `single<MyDataStore> { MyDataStoreImpl(...) }`
- [ ] DAO added to Room database entity list

### ViewModel Integration
- [ ] ViewModel constructor accepts `MyRepository`
- [ ] Repository called in suspend functions
- [ ] Results mapped to UI models
- [ ] Errors caught and emitted via SharedFlow

### Testing
- [ ] Repository tests with Mockito mocks
- [ ] Test local + remote data combining
- [ ] Test error handling
- [ ] Test entity mapping

---

## ✅ Adding Unit Tests

### ViewModel Test
- [ ] Created: `feature/myfeature/src/test/java/.../MyFeatureViewModelTest.kt`
- [ ] Mocked dependencies: `Repository`, `Navigator`, `TrackingRepository`
- [ ] Set up `Dispatchers.setMain(UnconfinedTestDispatcher())`
- [ ] Clean up: `Dispatchers.resetMain()` in @After
- [ ] Test happy path (state transition)
- [ ] Test empty state
- [ ] Test error case
- [ ] Test user action (navigation, logging)
- [ ] Using Turbine for Flow testing: `.test { awaitItem() }`
- [ ] Following Given/When/Then pattern

### Repository Test
- [ ] Created: `data/src/test/java/.../MyRepositoryTest.kt`
- [ ] Mocked Request + DataStore
- [ ] Test reading from local storage
- [ ] Test combining local + remote
- [ ] Test error handling
- [ ] Test write operations (create, update, delete)
- [ ] Verify repository calls both request and datastore

### Compose Preview Test
- [ ] Created: `ui/MyFeaturePreview.kt` or in main view file
- [ ] Preview for Loading state
- [ ] Preview for Data state (with mock data)
- [ ] Preview for Empty/Error states
- [ ] All previews wrapped in `PokeManiacTheme`
- [ ] Using `PersistentList` for collections

### Test Dependencies
- [ ] `build.gradle.kts` has: `junit`, `mockito-kotlin`, `coroutines-test`, `turbine`, `koin-test`
- [ ] Using correct imports

