## ✅ Architecture Compliance Check

### Dependency Direction
- [ ] Presentation layer ✓ imports Domain
- [ ] Presentation layer ✓ does NOT import Data/API/Database
- [ ] Domain layer ✓ imports nothing from app layers
- [ ] Data layer ✓ implements Domain interfaces

### State Management
- [ ] UI state: sealed class with multiple variants
- [ ] StateFlow: private mutable, public immutable
- [ ] SharedFlow: for one-shot events (errors)
- [ ] No boolean flags for state
- [ ] All data to render in state (complete)

### Screen/View Pattern
- [ ] Screen: `collectAsState()`, lifecycle, error handling
- [ ] View: no state collection, pure UI, preview
- [ ] Screen delegates to View
- [ ] All data passed as parameters to View

### Lifecycle
- [ ] `DisposableEffect` + `LifecycleEventObserver` in Screen
- [ ] Reload on `ON_START` event
- [ ] Proper cleanup on dispose

### ViewModel Pattern
- [ ] Constructor injection only
- [ ] No property initialization code
- [ ] Use `viewModelScope` for coroutines
- [ ] StateFlow for mutable state
- [ ] SharedFlow for events

### Naming Conventions
- [ ] Sealed state: `*UiState`
- [ ] ViewModel: `*ViewModel`
- [ ] Views: `*View`, `*Content`, `*TopBar`, `*Card`
- [ ] UI Models: `*UI` or `*Ui`
- [ ] Repository: `*Repository`, `*RepositoryImpl`
- [ ] Navigator: `*Navigator`, `*NavigatorImpl`
- [ ] Koin module: `*Module`
- [ ] Packages: `com.shodo.android.*`

