## ✅ Before Pushing to Remote

### Build & Compilation
- [ ] Project builds successfully: `./gradlew build`
- [ ] No lint warnings (or acceptable)
- [ ] No compilation errors

### Testing
- [ ] Unit tests pass: `./gradlew test`
- [ ] Android tests pass: `./gradlew connectedAndroidTest`
- [ ] Code coverage acceptable (if measured)

### Code Quality
- [ ] Code reviewed for issues
- [ ] No hardcoded values/strings
- [ ] No debug code left
- [ ] Proper error messages

### Documentation
- [ ] README updated (if needed)
- [ ] Complex logic commented
- [ ] KDoc for public APIs
- [ ] Architecture decisions documented

### Git
- [ ] Commits rebased/cleaned
- [ ] No merge conflicts
- [ ] Commit messages follow convention
- [ ] Branch is up-to-date with main

### Performance
- [ ] No obvious inefficiencies
- [ ] Database queries optimized
- [ ] API calls batched if possible
- [ ] Memory leaks checked (Compose)

