### Cleanup
- [ ] Removed debug code
- [ ] Removed unused imports
- [ ] Removed TODO comments (or created issues)

### Update Documentation
- [ ] Update feature list if applicable
- [ ] Update architecture diagrams if changed
- [ ] Update README if new setup steps
